    1   2   3   4   5   6   7

1   1   1   1   1   1   1   1 = 1
2   1   2   3   4   5   6   7 = (n+0)
3   1   3   6  10  15  21  28 = (n+0)(n+1)/2!
4   1   4  10  20  35  56  84 = (n+0)(n+1)(n+2)/3!
5   1   5  15  35  70 126 210 = (n+3)!/((n-1)!4!)
6   1   6  21  56 126 252 462
7   1   7  28  84 210 462 924

(n+3)×(n³+3n²+2n) = n⁴+3n³+2n²+3n³+

